comments: Bryant (LAL) touches the ball last before going out of bounds.
Toscano-Anderson (LAL) and Murray (ATL) come together in pursuit of the loose ball and marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Westbrook (LAL) initiates foot to foot contact with Murray (ATL) that affects his SQBR during the drive.
After the ball becomes loose, Westbrook (LAL) and Murray (ATL) mutually engage and marginal contact occurs.
Young (ATL) reaches in and marginal arm contact occurs with Bryant (LAL) during his play at the basket.
Young (LAL) commits a take foul on Westbrook (LAL).
Schroder (LAL) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Okongwu (ATL).
Griffin (ATL) commits a take foul on James (LAL).
Bogdanovic (ATL) does not overtly or abruptly extend his leg out as incidental contact occurs with Schroder (LAL) during the jump shot attempt.
